  "code": "stateDiagram-v2\n    [*] --> Invited: Admin creates User\n    Invited --> Active: User confirms email & sets password\n    \n    state \"Profile Setup\" as Setup {\n        Active --> IncompleteProfile: First Login\n        IncompleteProfile --> FillingData: User enters Bio/Phone\n        FillingData --> ProfileSubmitted: Save Changes\n    }\n\n    ProfileSubmitted --> StudentActive: Assign to Cohort/Advisor\n    \n    state \"Student Journey\" as Journey {\n        StudentActive --> InProgress: Starts Tasks\n        InProgress --> Graduated: All Tasks Done\n        InProgress --> DroppedOut: Admin Deactivates\n    }\n\n    Graduated --> Alumni: Final Status\n    DroppedOut --> [*]",
